      • sortTable

        public void sortTable(int col,
             javax.swing.table.TableColumnModel cm)
        Sorts the table in ascending order bases on the column given. If it was already sorted in ascending order, it will be sorted in descending order (and vice versa). It will also append a suffix to the header of the column being sorted indicating the order of the sort.
        Parameters:
        col - the column by which the table is sorted.
        cm - the TableColumnModel to use
